                     The meat counter at The Butcher Shop & Grill in Sandton, Johannesburg. It is a top choice for SABMiller Plc's Norman Adami who likes to drink beer and watch sports. The soccer World Cup ends on July 11. Photo: Renee Bonorchis/Bloomberg  
                   
    

                 
           
                            
                     
                     The meat counter at The Butcher Shop & Grill in Sandton, Johannesburg. The establishment offers South African fare like biltong and boerewor alongside well-aged rump and fillet steak. Patrons can choose their own slabs of meat from the counter, or have them packaged to take home. Photo: Renee Bonorchis/Bloomberg  
                   
    

                 
           
                                                 
                     
